# build OSRM
download your region from server, like http://download.geofabrik.de
run addfmreltags.pl, this will add special tags to ways, which are a part of relation (OSRM cannot handle relations at the moment)

# keep osrm in a loop like
while :; do osrm-routed /home/zaloha/db/tmp/osrm/bigslovakia-fmrel.osrm ; done 


